{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775823757775,"sessionID":"ses_288aad8b6ffedrU4WEylBNcrTt","part":{"id":"prt_d77554246001CymgxJ5QQ7vCUg","messageID":"msg_d77553686001BnwB6DilRfnO3y","sessionID":"ses_288aad8b6ffedrU4WEylBNcrTt","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_99f8c712312e4e4792db93e0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube project structure","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project at /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z. I need to understand:\n\n1. The overall project structure (top-level directories)\n2. The pkg/workloadmanager module in detail - read all Go files in it\n3. Any existing GC, cleanup, or timer-related code\n4. Any existing design documents (design.md, docs/, etc.)\n5. The AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRD types (look in pkg/apis/runtime/ or similar)\n6. Any existing configuration patterns used in the project\n\nBe very thorough - read all relevant Go source files in pkg/workloadmanager and related packages. Return the full content of key files and a summary of the architecture.","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_288aaaca6ffesB8IsV8b5OFGYO (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nNow I have a comprehensive understanding of the project. Here is my thorough analysis:\n\n---\n\n## AgentCube Project -- Comprehensive Architecture Analysis\n\n### 1. Overall Project Structure (Top-Level Directories)\n\n```\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/\n├── .sdd_prompt.md            # SDD prompt configuration\n├── changes/                   # Change proposals (AR-001 through AR-008)\n│   ├── AR-001/ through AR-008/   # Each has design.md, proposal.md, tasks.md\n├── ci-cd/                     # CI/CD design and spec\n├── cli-toolkit/               # CLI toolkit design\n├── client-go/                 # Generated Kubernetes client-go code\n│   ├── clientset/             # Typed clientset\n│   ├── informers/             # Shared informers\n│   └── listers/               # Listers\n├── code-execution/            # Code execution module design\n├── coverage.out               # Test coverage output\n├── delta-spec.md              # Delta specification\n├── deployment/                # Deployment design\n├── design.md                  # Top-level design doc (AR-003: CRD shared types)\n├── go.mod                     # Go module: github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube (Go 1.25.0)\n├── go.sum\n├── idle-cleanup/              # Idle cleanup (agentd) design\n├── integrations/              # Integration design\n├── pkg/                       # Go packages\n│   ├── apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ # CRD type definitions\n│   └── workloadmanager/       # Core workload manager module\n├── project.md                 # Project context document\n├── python-sdk/                # Python SDK design\n├── sandbox-orchestration/     # Sandbox orchestration design\n├── session-routing/           # Session routing design\n├── session-store/             # Session store (Redis/Valkey) design\n├── test_spec.md               # Test specification\n└── testing/                   # Testing manifests\n```\n\n### 2. pkg/workloadmanager Module -- Complete Analysis\n\nThe workloadmanager module is organized into three sub-packages:\n\n#### 2.1 `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/` -- Kubernetes Reconciler Controller (AR-007)\n\n**Files:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/reconciler.go` (200 lines)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/types.go` (67 lines)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/agentruntime.go` (127 lines)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/codeinterpreter.go` (105 lines)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/pod.go` (100 lines)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/sync.go` (125 lines)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/event_handlers.go` (165 lines)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/metrics.go` (86 lines)\n\n**Key Architecture:**\n- `SandboxReconciler` struct: The main reconciler using the standard Kubernetes Informer + Workqueue pattern\n- Uses `SharedInformerFactory` to watch AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter, and Pod resources\n- Workqueue with exponential backoff (5s initial, 5min max, 15 max retries)\n- Default 2 worker goroutines\n- Graceful shutdown with 30s cache sync timeout and 30s queue drain timeout\n\n**Reconciliation Flow:**\n1. Event callbacks (Add/Update/Delete) enqueue keys via `cache.MetaNamespaceKeyFunc`\n2. Workers call `processNextWorkItem()` -> `syncHandler(key)`\n3. `syncHandler` tries AR lister -> CI lister -> Pod lister in order\n4. Each resource type has its own reconcile function that syncs K8s state to the Store\n\n**State Mapping (K8s Conditions -> Store Status):**\n| Ready Condition | Store Status |\n|---|---|\n| Missing | `pending` |\n| `Unknown` | `pending` |\n| `True` | `running` |\n| `False` + `Terminated` | `terminated` |\n| `False` + other | `pending` |\n\n**Metrics (Prometheus):**\n- `reconcile_total` (Counter, labels: resource_type, result)\n- `reconcile_duration_seconds` (Histogram, labels: resource_type)\n- `reconcile_errors_total` (Counter, labels: resource_type, error_type)\n- `workqueue_depth` (Gauge)\n- `workqueue_adds_total` (Counter, labels: resource_type)\n\n#### 2.2 `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/` -- HTTP Handlers\n\n**Files:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_create.go` (693 lines)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_delete.go` (216 lines)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_lifecycle.go` (343 lines)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/models.go` (57 lines)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/constants.go` (53 lines)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_lifecycle_test.go` (696 lines)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_delete_test.go` (387 lines)\n\n**Key Components:**\n\n**SandboxCreateHandler:** Creates sandboxes from AgentRuntime or CodeInterpreter templates\n- Generates UUID session IDs and random sandbox names (`{workloadName}-{8 random chars}`)\n- Builds unstructured Sandbox CRs with labels and annotations\n- Supports WarmPool (SandboxClaim) when `WarmPoolSize > 0`\n- Injects PicoD auth env when `AuthMode == picod`\n- Waits for sandbox to become Running via `SandboxReconcilerWatcher` (2min timeout)\n- Resolves Pod IP and builds EntryPoints\n- Rollback on failure\n\n**SandboxDeleteHandler:** Deletes sandboxes by session ID or by name\n- Two endpoints: `DeleteSandbox` (by session) and `DeleteSandboxByName` (by name+namespace)\n- Idempotent: NotFound on CR deletion is treated as success\n- Order: Delete CR first, then clean Store entry\n- Supports per-user dynamic clients when auth is enabled\n\n**LifecycleManager:** Background GC and lifecycle management\n- **Timer-based cleanup loop** with configurable `CheckInterval` (default 5min) and `DefaultTTL` (default 8h)\n- `cleanupExpiredSandboxes()`: Lists all sandboxes, checks expiration via `isExpired()`, deletes expired ones\n- Expiration logic: `ExpiresAt` if set, otherwise `CreatedAt + DefaultTTL`\n- HTTP endpoints: `GetSandboxStatus`, `ListSandboxes` (with namespace/status filters), `ExtendSandboxTTL` (max 24h extension)\n- Uses `time.NewTicker` for the cleanup loop\n\n#### 2.3 `pkg/workloadmanager/response/` -- HTTP Response Helpers\n\n**Files:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/response/response.go` (45 lines)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/response/response_test.go` (110 lines)\n\nStandardized JSON responses: `SuccessResponse{Data, Message}`, `ErrorResponse{Error, Code, RequestID}`.\n\n### 3. GC, Cleanup, and Timer-Related Code\n\n**Existing GC mechanisms (three layers):**\n\n1. **LifecycleManager GC Loop** (`handler/sandbox_lifecycle.go`):\n   - `time.NewTicker(m.checkInterval)` -- default 5 minutes\n   - `cleanupExpiredSandboxes()`: Lists all sandboxes from Store, checks `isExpired()`, deletes via dynamic client\n   - Expiration: `ExpiresAt` if set, else `CreatedAt + DefaultTTL` (8 hours)\n   - DefaultTTL: 8 hours, CheckInterval: 5 minutes (both configurable via `LifecycleManagerDeps`)\n\n2. **Reconciler Event-Driven Cleanup** (`reconciler/agentruntime.go`, `reconciler/codeinterpreter.go`):\n   - When CR has `DeletionTimestamp != nil`: calls `store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID()`\n   - When status becomes `terminated`: calls `store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID()`\n   - This is the AR-007 instant cleanup (complements the GC loop)\n\n3. **Agentd Idle Cleanup Controller** (documented in `idle-cleanup/design.md`):\n   - Separate controller that watches Sandbox CRs\n   - Reads `last-activity-time` annotation\n   - Deletes sandbox when `now > lastActivity + SessionExpirationTimeout` (15 minutes)\n   - Requeues with `time.Until(expirationTime)` for precision\n\n**TTL/Timeout Constants:**\n| Constant | Value | Location |\n|---|---|---|\n| `DefaultSandboxTTL` | 8 (hours) | `handler/constants.go` |\n| `DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout` | 15 (minutes) | `handler/constants.go` |\n| `SessionExpirationTimeout` | 15 minutes | `idle-cleanup/design.md` (agentd) |\n| `gcOnceTimeout` | 2 minutes | `sandbox-orchestration/design.md` |\n| `GCInterval` | 15 seconds | `sandbox-orchestration/design.md` |\n| `CheckInterval` (LifecycleManager) | 5 minutes (default) | `handler/sandbox_lifecycle.go` |\n| `DefaultTTL` (LifecycleManager) | 8 hours (default) | `handler/sandbox_lifecycle.go` |\n\n**Key Gaps Identified (from AR-008 proposal):**\n- No idle timeout cleanup in LifecycleManager (only ExpiresAt/CreatedAt+TTL)\n- No orphan CR scanning (CRs without Store entries)\n- No ghost entry cleanup (Store entries without CRs)\n- No GC metrics exposure\n- Uses `log.Printf` instead of structured logging\n\n### 4. Design Documents\n\n| Document | Path | Content |\n|---|---|---|\n| Main Design | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md` | AR-003: CRD shared types extraction |\n| Project Context | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/project.md` | Architecture overview, tech stack |\n| Sandbox Orchestration | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/sandbox-orchestration/design.md` | Full system design, all packages |\n| Idle Cleanup | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/idle-cleanup/design.md` | Agentd idle cleanup controller |\n| AR-006 Design | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/design.md` | Sandbox deletion + GC |\n| AR-007 Design | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-007/design.md` | K8s Reconciler controller (fully implemented) |\n| AR-008 Design | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-008/design.md` | Sandbox GC cleanup (skeleton/empty) |\n| AR-008 Proposal | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-008/proposal.md` | GC enhancement proposal (detailed) |\n\n### 5. AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRD Types\n\n**Location:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n\n**API Group:** `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n\n**AgentRuntime** (`agent_type.go`):\n```go\ntype AgentRuntime struct {\n    Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec\n    Status AgentRuntimeStatus\n}\ntype AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n    Ports              []TargetPort\n    Template           *SandboxTemplate    // PodSpec template\n    SessionTimeout     *metav1.Duration    // idle timeout (default 15m)\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration    // max TTL (default 8h)\n}\ntype SandboxTemplate struct {\n    Labels, Annotations map[string]string\n    Spec                corev1.PodSpec\n}\ntype AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition\n}\n```\n\n**CodeInterpreter** (`codeinterpreter_types.go`):\n```go\ntype CodeInterpreter struct {\n    Spec   CodeInterpreterSpec\n    Status CodeInterpreterStatus\n}\ntype CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n    Ports              []TargetPort\n    Template           *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate\n    SessionTimeout     *metav1.Duration\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration\n    WarmPoolSize       *int32           // enables SandboxClaim mode\n    AuthMode           AuthModeType     // \"picod\" or \"none\"\n}\ntype CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate struct {\n    Labels, Annotations  map[string]string\n    RuntimeClassName     *string\n    Image                string\n    ImagePullPolicy      corev1.PullPolicy\n    ImagePullSecrets     []corev1.LocalObjectReference\n    Environment          []corev1.EnvVar\n    Command, Args        []string\n    Resources            corev1.ResourceRequirements\n}\n```\n\n**Shared Types** (`shared_types.go`):\n```go\ntype ProtocolType string  // \"HTTP\", \"HTTPS\"\ntype TargetPort struct {\n    PathPrefix string\n    Name       string\n    Port       uint32\n    Protocol   ProtocolType\n}\ntype AuthModeType string  // \"picod\", \"none\"\n```\n\n### 6. Configuration Patterns\n\n**Dependency Injection Pattern:** All major components use `*Deps` structs:\n- `ReconcilerDeps` -- for SandboxReconciler\n- `LifecycleManagerDeps` -- for LifecycleManager\n- `SandboxCreateHandlerDeps` -- for SandboxCreateHandler\n- `SandboxDeleteHandlerDeps` -- for SandboxDeleteHandler\n\n**Zero-Value Safety:** Optional fields default safely:\n- `Workers == 0` -> defaults to 2\n- `MetricsRecorder == nil` -> all metric calls are no-ops\n- `CheckInterval == 0` -> defaults to 5 minutes\n- `DefaultTTL == 0` -> defaults to 8 hours\n\n**Constants Organization** (`handler/constants.go`):\n- GVR variables: `AgentRuntimeGVR`, `CodeInterpreterGVR`, `SandboxGVR`, `SandboxClaimGVR`\n- Kind constants: `AgentRuntimeKind`, `CodeInterpreterKind`, `SandboxesKind`, `SandboxClaimsKind`\n- Label keys: `LabelManagedBy`, `LabelSessionID`, `LabelWorkloadName`, `LabelSandboxName`\n- Annotation keys: `AnnotationIdleTimeout`, `AnnotationSandboxPodName`\n- Defaults: `DefaultSandboxTTL = 8` (hours), `DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout = 15` (minutes)\n\n**Store Interface Pattern:** Two slightly different Store interfaces exist:\n- `reconciler/types.go`: `StoreSandbox(ctx, sessionID, info)`, `UpdateSandbox(ctx, sessionID, info)`, `DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)`, `GetSandbox(ctx, sessionID)`, `ListSandboxes(ctx)`\n- `handler/sandbox_create.go`: `StoreSandbox(ctx, info)`, `UpdateSandbox(ctx, sessionID, info)`, `GetSandbox(ctx, sessionID)`, `DeleteSandbox(ctx, sessionID)`, `ListSandboxes(ctx)`\n\n**Key Architecture Summary:**\n\n```\nClient/SDK/CLI\n  -> WorkloadManager (Gin HTTP :8080)\n       -> SandboxCreateHandler  -- Creates Sandbox CRs from templates\n       -> SandboxDeleteHandler  -- Deletes Sandbox CRs + Store entries\n       -> LifecycleManager      -- Background GC (5min ticker, TTL/idle expiry)\n       -> SandboxReconciler     -- K8s Informer+Workqueue controller\n            -> Watches: AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter, Pod\n            -> Syncs: K8s CR status <-> Store session state\n            -> Metrics: Prometheus counters/histograms\n       -> Store (Redis/Valkey)  -- Session state persistence\n  -> K8s API: Sandbox CRs, SandboxClaims, Pods\n  -> Agentd (separate)          -- Idle cleanup controller (15min timeout)\n```\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_288aaaca6ffesB8IsV8b5OFGYO","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775823573846,"end":1775823757772}}}}
